class solution:
    def main(self):
        print("counted number is ..")
        self.insert = ""
        self.count = [0,0,0,0] # A C G T
        for i in self.insert:
            if i == "A":
                self.count[0] += 1
            elif i == "C":
                self.count[1] += 1

            elif i == "G":
                self.count[2] += 1

            elif i == "T":
                self.count[3] += 1
        print(self.count[0], self.count[1], self.count[2], self.count[3])
        #print(len(self.count))
        ans = [0] * 4
        ans[0] = self.count[0]
        ans[1] = self.count[1]
        ans[2] = self.count[2]
        ans[3] = self.count[3]
        print(ans)
        return ans

p = solution()
p.main()
